From the node you wish to join to this cluster, run the following:
microk8s join 10.171.70.93:25000/09dfb3656d9307d8f33c26e617fb7fca/6c50aaf4eb62

Use the '--worker' flag to join a node as a worker not running the control plane, eg:
microk8s join 10.171.70.93:25000/09dfb3656d9307d8f33c26e617fb7fca/6c50aaf4eb62 --worker

If the node you are adding is not reachable through the default interface you can use one of the following:
microk8s join 10.171.70.93:25000/09dfb3656d9307d8f33c26e617fb7fca/6c50aaf4eb62
microk8s join fd42:94:e41e:89e9:216:3eff:fe6a:776b:25000/09dfb3656d9307d8f33c26e617fb7fca/6c50aaf4eb62
